{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":856,"text":"I am no designer, nope, no way."},{"time":4707,"text":"My dad was,"},{"time":6523,"text":"which is kind of an interesting way to grow up."},{"time":9115,"text":"I had to figure out what it is my dad did"},{"time":13290,"text":"and why it was important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15090,"text":"Dad talked a lot about bad design when we were growing up,"},{"time":18251,"text":"you know, \"Bad design is just people not thinking, John,\" he would say"},{"time":23221,"text":"whenever a kid would be injured by a rotary lawn mower"},{"time":25684,"text":"or, say, a typewriter ribbon would get tangled"},{"time":28634,"text":"or an eggbeater would get jammed in the kitchen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31027,"text":"You know, \"Design -- bad design, there's just no excuse for it."},{"time":36546,"text":"It's letting stuff happen without thinking about it."},{"time":39154,"text":"Every object should be about something, John."},{"time":42517,"text":"It should imagine a user."},{"time":43955,"text":"It should cast that user in a story starring the user and the object."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48922,"text":"Good design,\" my dad said, \"is about supplying intent.\""},{"time":54163,"text":"That's what he said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56818,"text":"Dad helped design the control panels for the IBM 360 computer."},{"time":60739,"text":"That was a big deal; that was important. He worked for Kodak for a while; that was important."},{"time":64739,"text":"He designed chairs and desks and other office equipment for Steelcase; that was important."},{"time":70295,"text":"I knew design was important in my house because, for heaven's sake, it put food on our table, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75333,"text":"And design was in everything my dad did."},{"time":77705,"text":"He had a Dixieland jazz band when we were growing up,"},{"time":80862,"text":"and he would always cover Louis Armstrong tunes."},{"time":83558,"text":"And I would ask him every once in a while,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":85286,"text":"\"Dad, do you want it to sound like the record?\""},{"time":88197,"text":"We had lots of old jazz records lying around the house."},{"time":90350,"text":"And he said, \"No, never, John, never."},{"time":92647,"text":"The song is just a given, that's how you have to think about it."},{"time":95374,"text":"You gotta make it your own. You gotta design it."},{"time":98059,"text":"Show everyone what you intend,\" is what he said."},{"time":102056,"text":"\"Doing that, acting by design, is what we all should be doing."},{"time":106345,"text":"It's where we all belong.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":108454,"text":"All of us? Designers?"},{"time":111879,"text":"Oh, oh, Dad. Oh, Dad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116813,"text":"The song is just a given."},{"time":118478,"text":"It's how you cover it that matters."},{"time":120966,"text":"Well, let's hold on to that thought for just a minute."},{"time":123062,"text":"It's kind of like this wheelchair I'm in, right?"},{"time":125965,"text":"The original tune? It's a little scary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127990,"text":"\"Ooh, what happened to that dude?"},{"time":130654,"text":"He can't walk. Anybody know the story?"},{"time":133765,"text":"Anybody?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":135671,"text":"I don't like to talk about this very much, but I'll tell you guys the story today."},{"time":140958,"text":"All right, exactly 36 years ago this week, that's right,"},{"time":144808,"text":"I was in a poorly designed automobile"},{"time":146750,"text":"that hit a poorly designed guardrail"},{"time":150671,"text":"on a poorly designed road in Pennsylvania,"},{"time":153254,"text":"and plummeted down a 200-foot embankment"},{"time":158047,"text":"and killed two people in the car."},{"time":160254,"text":"But ever since then, the wheelchair has been a given in my life."},{"time":164733,"text":"My life, at the mercy of good design and bad design."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169869,"text":"Think about it. Now, in design terms,"},{"time":172272,"text":"a wheelchair is a very difficult object."},{"time":175270,"text":"It mostly projects tragedy and fear and misfortune,"},{"time":179438,"text":"and it projects that message, that story, so strongly"},{"time":182229,"text":"that it almost blots out anything else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184488,"text":"I roll swiftly through an airport, right?"},{"time":187966,"text":"And moms grab their kids out of the way and say, \"Don't stare!\""},{"time":191950,"text":"The poor kid, you know, has this terrified look on his face, God knows what they think."},{"time":196149,"text":"And for decades, I'm going,"},{"time":198318,"text":"why does this happen? What can I do about it? How can I change this? I mean there must be something."},{"time":202798,"text":"So I would roll, I'd make no eye contact -- just kinda frown, right?"},{"time":207957,"text":"Or I'd dress up really, really sharply or something."},{"time":213389,"text":"Or I'd make eye contact with everyone --"},{"time":215266,"text":"that was really creepy; that didn't work at all."},{"time":217758,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":219671,"text":"You know anything, I'd try. I wouldn't shower for a week -- nothing worked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223526,"text":"Nothing whatsoever worked until a few years ago,"},{"time":227510,"text":"my six-year-old daughters were looking at this wheelchair catalog that I had, and they said,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":231850,"text":"\"Oh, Dad! Dad! Look, you gotta get these, these flashy wheels -- you gotta get 'em!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":236974,"text":"And I said, \"Oh, girls, Dad is a very important journalist,"},{"time":241087,"text":"that just wouldn't do at all.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":243653,"text":"And of course, they immediately concluded,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":245598,"text":"\"Oh, what a bummer, Dad. Journalists aren't allowed to have flashy wheels."},{"time":250765,"text":"I mean, how important could you be then?\" they said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255243,"text":"I went, \"Wait a minute, all right, right -- I'll get the wheels.\" Purely out of protest,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":260205,"text":"I got the flashy wheels, and I installed them and --"},{"time":265123,"text":"check this out. Could I have my special light cue please?"},{"time":268651,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":270173,"text":"Look at that!"},{"time":273104,"text":"Now ... look at, look at this! Look at this!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275569,"text":"So what you are looking at here"},{"time":279016,"text":"has completely changed my life,"},{"time":282103,"text":"I mean totally changed my life."},{"time":285080,"text":"Instead of blank stares and awkwardness,"},{"time":287952,"text":"now it is pointing and smiling!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291436,"text":"People going, \"Awesome wheels, dude! Those are awesome!"},{"time":295504,"text":"I mean, I want some of those wheels!\" Little kids say,"},{"time":298104,"text":"\"Can I have a ride?\""},{"time":300240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302115,"text":"And of course there's the occasional person --"},{"time":304632,"text":"usually a middle-aged male who will say,"},{"time":306448,"text":"\"Oh, those wheels are great!"},{"time":308089,"text":"I guess they're for safety, right?\""},{"time":310379,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":312728,"text":"No! They're not for safety."},{"time":318696,"text":"No, no, no, no, no."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320576,"text":"What's the difference here,"},{"time":322353,"text":"the wheelchair with no lights"},{"time":324160,"text":"and the wheelchair with lights?"},{"time":325890,"text":"The difference is intent."},{"time":329672,"text":"That's right, that's right; I'm no longer a victim."},{"time":333329,"text":"I chose to change the situation -- I'm the Commander of the Starship Wheelchair with the phaser wheels in the front. Right?"},{"time":339241,"text":"Intent changes the picture completely."},{"time":343616,"text":"I choose to enhance"},{"time":345433,"text":"this rolling experience"},{"time":347376,"text":"with a simple design element."},{"time":351080,"text":"Acting with intent."},{"time":353288,"text":"It conveys authorship."},{"time":355504,"text":"It suggests that someone is driving."},{"time":358584,"text":"It's reassuring; people are drawn to it."},{"time":361592,"text":"Someone making the experience their own."},{"time":365104,"text":"Covering the tragic tune"},{"time":367344,"text":"with something different,"},{"time":370240,"text":"something radically different."},{"time":373449,"text":"People respond to that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375496,"text":"Now it seems simple, but actually I think"},{"time":378288,"text":"in our society and culture in general,"},{"time":380513,"text":"we have a huge problem with intent."},{"time":382576,"text":"Now go with me here. Look at this guy. You know who this is?"},{"time":385936,"text":"It's Anders Breivik. Now, if he intended to kill"},{"time":389952,"text":"in Olso, Norway last year,"},{"time":391688,"text":"dozens and dozens of young people --"},{"time":394048,"text":"if he intended to do that,"},{"time":395760,"text":"he's a vicious criminal. We punish him."},{"time":398344,"text":"Life in prison. Death penalty in the United States, not so much in Norway."},{"time":401713,"text":"But, if he instead acted out of a delusional fantasy,"},{"time":406064,"text":"if he was motivated by some random mental illness,"},{"time":411048,"text":"he's in a completely different category."},{"time":413494,"text":"We may put him away for life, but"},{"time":415281,"text":"we watch him clinically."},{"time":417320,"text":"It's a completely different domain."},{"time":420769,"text":"As an intentional murderer,"},{"time":423241,"text":"Anders Breivik is merely evil."},{"time":426280,"text":"But as a dysfunctional,"},{"time":428465,"text":"as a dysfunctional murderer/psychotic,"},{"time":430713,"text":"he's something much more complicated."},{"time":432672,"text":"He's the breath of some \n"},{"time":434432,"text":"primitive, ancient chaos."},{"time":437832,"text":"He's the random state of nature"},{"time":439816,"text":"we emerged from."},{"time":441346,"text":"He's something very, very different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443616,"text":"It's as though intent is an essential component for humanity."},{"time":447353,"text":"It's what we're supposed to do somehow."},{"time":449672,"text":"We're supposed to act with intent."},{"time":452400,"text":"We're supposed to do things by design."},{"time":454856,"text":"Intent is a marker for civilization."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459696,"text":"Now here's an example a little closer to home:"},{"time":462288,"text":"My family is all about intent."},{"time":464664,"text":"You can probably tell there are two sets of twins,"},{"time":467872,"text":"the result of IVF technology, in vitro fertilization technology,"},{"time":472120,"text":"due to some physical limitations I won't go into."},{"time":474755,"text":"Anyway, in vitro technology, IVF,"},{"time":477808,"text":"is about as intentional as agriculture."},{"time":480812,"text":"Let me tell you, some of you may have the experience."},{"time":482968,"text":"In fact, the whole technology of sperm extraction"},{"time":485912,"text":"for spinal cord-injured males was invented by a veterinarian."},{"time":490360,"text":"I met the dude. He's a great guy."},{"time":492642,"text":"He carried this big leather bag full of sperm probes for"},{"time":497584,"text":"all of the animals that he'd worked with,"},{"time":499880,"text":"all the different animals."},{"time":501379,"text":"Probes he designed,"},{"time":503511,"text":"and in fact, he was really, really proud of these probes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506512,"text":"He would say, \"You're right between horse and squirrel, John.\""},{"time":510282,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":513520,"text":"But anyway, so when my wife and I decided"},{"time":519192,"text":"to upgrade our early middle age -- we had four kids, after all --"},{"time":522241,"text":"with a little different technology"},{"time":524232,"text":"that I won't explain in too much detail here --"},{"time":527112,"text":"my urologist assured me I had nothing whatsoever to worry about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531370,"text":"\"No need for birth control, Doc, are you sure about that?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":533946,"text":"\"John, John, I looked at your chart."},{"time":537506,"text":"From your sperm tests we can"},{"time":539763,"text":"confidently say that"},{"time":541771,"text":"you're basically a form of birth control.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":544493,"text":"Well!"},{"time":547771,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":551363,"text":"What a liberating thought! Yes!"},{"time":554738,"text":"And after a couple very liberating weekends,"},{"time":557803,"text":"my wife and I,"},{"time":559243,"text":"utilizing some cutting-edge erectile technology"},{"time":563131,"text":"that is certainly worthy of a TEDTalk someday"},{"time":565715,"text":"but I won't get into it now,"},{"time":567746,"text":"we noticed some familiar, if unexpected, symptoms."},{"time":572498,"text":"I wasn't exactly a form of birth control."},{"time":576158,"text":"Look at that font there. My wife was so pissed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":579738,"text":"I mean, did a designer come up with that?"},{"time":581283,"text":"No, I don't think a designer did come up with that."},{"time":583515,"text":"In fact, maybe that's the problem."},{"time":585730,"text":"And so, little Ajax was born."},{"time":588411,"text":"He's like our other children,"},{"time":590680,"text":"but the experience is completely different."},{"time":592458,"text":"It's something like my accident, right?"},{"time":596698,"text":"He came out of nowhere."},{"time":597973,"text":"But we all had to change,"},{"time":599579,"text":"but not just react to the given;"},{"time":602260,"text":"we bend to this new experience with intent."},{"time":606819,"text":"We're five now. Five."},{"time":610891,"text":"Facing the given with intent. Doing things by design."},{"time":614803,"text":"Hey, the name Ajax -- you can't get much more intentional than that, right?"},{"time":619035,"text":"We're really hoping he thanks us for that later on."},{"time":623275,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":625108,"text":"But I never became a designer. No, no, no, no. Never attempted. Never even close."},{"time":629007,"text":"I did love some great designs as I was growing up:"},{"time":633645,"text":"The HP 35S calculator -- God, I loved that thing. Oh God, I wish I had one."},{"time":638012,"text":"Man, I love that thing."},{"time":641462,"text":"I could afford that."},{"time":642685,"text":"Other designs I really couldn't afford, like the 1974 911 Targa."},{"time":647324,"text":"In school, I studied nothing close to design or engineering;"},{"time":650789,"text":"I studied useless things like the Classics,"},{"time":653108,"text":"but there were some lessons even there --"},{"time":654925,"text":"this guy, Plato, it turns out he's a designer."},{"time":658189,"text":"He designed a state in \"The Republic,\""},{"time":661612,"text":"a design never implemented."},{"time":663103,"text":"Listen to one of the design features"},{"time":664788,"text":"of Plato's Government 4.0:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":667812,"text":"\"The State in which the rulers are most reluctant to govern"},{"time":672372,"text":"is always the best and most quietly governed,"},{"time":675308,"text":"and the State in which they are most eager, the worst.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":679380,"text":"Well, got that wrong, didn't we?"},{"time":682324,"text":"But look at that statement; it's all about intent. That's what I love about it."},{"time":686621,"text":"But consider what Plato is doing here. What is he doing?"},{"time":690076,"text":"It's a grand idea of design -- a huge idea of design,"},{"time":693596,"text":"common to all of the voices of religion and philosophy"},{"time":697313,"text":"that emerged in the Classical period."},{"time":699553,"text":"What was going on then?"},{"time":700986,"text":"They were trying to answer the question of"},{"time":703122,"text":"what would human beings do now that they were no longer simply trying to survive?"},{"time":708088,"text":"As the human race emerged from a prehistoric chaos,"},{"time":712529,"text":"a confrontation with random, brutal nature,"},{"time":716953,"text":"they suddenly had a moment to think -- and there was a lot to think about."},{"time":720537,"text":"All of a sudden, human existence needed an intent."},{"time":724664,"text":"Human life needed a reason."},{"time":727379,"text":"Reality itself needed a designer."},{"time":730401,"text":"The given was replaced"},{"time":732793,"text":"by various aspects of intent,"},{"time":735417,"text":"by various designs,"},{"time":738001,"text":"by various gods."},{"time":740281,"text":"Gods we're still fighting about. Oh yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":744225,"text":"Today we don't confront the chaos of nature."},{"time":747385,"text":"Today it is the chaos of humanity's impact on the Earth itself that we confront."},{"time":753265,"text":"This young discipline called design, I think,"},{"time":756545,"text":"is in fact the emerging ethos"},{"time":759812,"text":"formulating and then answering a very new question:"},{"time":762730,"text":"What shall we do now"},{"time":764329,"text":"in the face of the chaos that we have created?"},{"time":768072,"text":"What shall we do?"},{"time":769976,"text":"How shall we inscribe intent"},{"time":772442,"text":"on all the objects we create,"},{"time":774745,"text":"on all the circumstances we create,"},{"time":776721,"text":"on all the places we change?"},{"time":779328,"text":"The consequences of a planet with 7 billion people and counting."},{"time":783456,"text":"That's the tune we're all covering today, all of us."},{"time":787825,"text":"And we can't just imitate the past. No."},{"time":790361,"text":"That won't do."},{"time":793195,"text":"That won't do at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794970,"text":"Here's my favorite design moment:"},{"time":797977,"text":"In the city of Kinshasa in Zaire in the 1990s,"},{"time":801385,"text":"I was working for ABC News, and I was reporting on"},{"time":803673,"text":"the fall of Mobutu Sese Seko, the dictator, the brutal dictator in Zaire,"},{"time":807817,"text":"who raped and pillaged that country."},{"time":809817,"text":"There was rioting in the middle of Kinshasa."},{"time":812385,"text":"The place was falling apart; it was a horrible, horrible place,"},{"time":815866,"text":"and I needed to go and explore the center of Kinshasa"},{"time":819737,"text":"to report on the rioting and the looting."},{"time":821760,"text":"People were carrying off vehicles, carrying off pieces of buildings."},{"time":825546,"text":"Soldiers were in the streets shooting at looters and herding some in mass arrests."},{"time":830241,"text":"In the middle of this chaos, I'm rolling around in a wheelchair,"},{"time":833755,"text":"and I was completely invisible. Completely."},{"time":837505,"text":"I was in a wheelchair; I didn't look like a looter."},{"time":840275,"text":"I was in a wheelchair; I didn't look like a journalist, particularly, at least from their perspective."},{"time":846457,"text":"And I didn't look like a soldier, that's for sure."},{"time":848697,"text":"I was part of this sort of background noise of the misery of Zaire, completely invisible."},{"time":854992,"text":"And all of a sudden, from around a corner, comes this young man, paralyzed, just like me,"},{"time":860089,"text":"in this metal and wood and leather"},{"time":863809,"text":"pedal, three-wheel tricycle-wheelchair device,"},{"time":868834,"text":"and he pedals up to me as fast as he can."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871298,"text":"He goes, \"Hey, mister! Mister!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":873073,"text":"And I looked at him --"},{"time":875370,"text":"he didn't know any other English than that, but we didn't need English, no, no, no, no, no."},{"time":878954,"text":"We sat there and compared wheels and tires and spokes and tubes."},{"time":884825,"text":"And I looked at his whacky pedal mechanism;"},{"time":888250,"text":"he was full of pride over his design."},{"time":891490,"text":"I wish I could show you that contraption."},{"time":893339,"text":"His smile, our glow"},{"time":895466,"text":"as we talked a universal language"},{"time":897977,"text":"of design,"},{"time":900689,"text":"invisible to the chaos around us."},{"time":903506,"text":"His machine: homemade, bolted, rusty, comical."},{"time":907562,"text":"My machine: American-made, confident, sleek."},{"time":910860,"text":"He was particularly proud of the comfortable seat, really comfortable seat"},{"time":915082,"text":"he had made in his chariot"},{"time":916998,"text":"and its beautiful fabric fringe around the edge."},{"time":921425,"text":"Oh, I wish I'd had those sparkly wheels back then to have shown him, man!"},{"time":925409,"text":"He would have loved those! Oh yeah."},{"time":928154,"text":"He would have understood those;"},{"time":929746,"text":"a chariot of pure intent -- think about it --"},{"time":933214,"text":"in a city out of control."},{"time":935826,"text":"Design blew it all away for a moment."},{"time":938874,"text":"We spoke for a few minutes and then each of us vanished back into the chaos."},{"time":943018,"text":"He went back to the streets of Kinshasa;"},{"time":945437,"text":"I went to my hotel. And I think of him now, now ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":951419,"text":"And I pose this question."},{"time":954481,"text":"An object imbued with intent --"},{"time":958034,"text":"it has power,"},{"time":959698,"text":"it's treasure, we're drawn to it."},{"time":963098,"text":"An object devoid of intent --"},{"time":965730,"text":"it's random, it's imitative,"},{"time":968242,"text":"it repels us. It's like a piece of junk mail to be thrown away."},{"time":971922,"text":"This is what we must demand of our lives,"},{"time":976673,"text":"of our objects, of our things, of our circumstances:"},{"time":980498,"text":"living with intent."},{"time":983594,"text":"And I have to say"},{"time":985698,"text":"that on that score, I have a very unfair advantage over all of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":990729,"text":"And I want to explain it to you now because this is a very special day."},{"time":996434,"text":"Thirty-six years ago at nearly this moment,"},{"time":1001369,"text":"a 19-year-old boy awoke from a coma"},{"time":1005525,"text":"to ask a nurse a question,"},{"time":1007322,"text":"but the nurse was already there with an answer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1009802,"text":"\"You've had a terrible accident, young man. You've broken your back."},{"time":1013505,"text":"You'll never walk again.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1015146,"text":"I said, \"I know all that -- what day is it?\""},{"time":1020762,"text":"You see, I knew that the car had gone over the guardrail on the 28th of February,"},{"time":1027786,"text":"and I knew that 1976 was a leap year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1031435,"text":"\"Nurse! Is this the 28th or the 29th?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1036145,"text":"And she looked at me and said,"},{"time":1038138,"text":"\"It's March 1st.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1040713,"text":"And I went, \"Oh my God."},{"time":1043194,"text":"I've got some catching up to do!\""},{"time":1045730,"text":"And from that moment, I knew"},{"time":1048402,"text":"the given was that accident;"},{"time":1051650,"text":"I had no option but to make up"},{"time":1055338,"text":"this new life without walking."},{"time":1058394,"text":"Intent -- a life with intent --"},{"time":1062202,"text":"lived by design,"},{"time":1064026,"text":"covering the original"},{"time":1065642,"text":"with something better."},{"time":1067202,"text":"It's something for all of us to do or find a way to do in these times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072282,"text":"To get back to this,"},{"time":1075624,"text":"to get back to design,"},{"time":1077760,"text":"and as my daddy suggested a long time ago,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1081161,"text":"\"Make the song your own, John."},{"time":1084448,"text":"Show everybody what you intend.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1103430,"text":"Daddy,"},{"time":1105729,"text":"this one's for you."},{"time":1107677,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1112457,"text":"♫ Jo Jo was a man who thought he was a loner ♫"},{"time":1116665,"text":"♫ but he was another man. ♫"},{"time":1118985,"text":"♫ Jo Jo left his home in Tucson, Arizona to attend a California bash. ♫"},{"time":1125170,"text":"♫ Get back, get back, ♫"},{"time":1128113,"text":"♫ get back to where you once belonged. ♫"},{"time":1131393,"text":"♫ Get back, get back, ♫"},{"time":1134257,"text":"♫ get back to where you once belonged. ♫"},{"time":1143720,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}